{"tid":1481537,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有人說平行線最可怕，但我認為最可怕的是相交線。明明他們有過交集，卻總會在以後某個時刻相互遠離，而且越走越遠。","createTime":"2019-08-17T17:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T04:09:55.000Z","uid":295218,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9640d43fe9c88417323a3f2b03ed81255ddf8d","tid":1481537,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:54:47.000Z","msg":"其實有無巴絲試過等一個人八年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時候好懷疑自己係咪病態？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當初分手嘅時候<br />\n我地承諾過如果十年後再次相遇，我地就重新開始<br />\n我知呢句只係為咗大家可以舒服啲分手而講<br />\n雖然一直遇過好多好對象<br />\n但我真係忘記唔到佢<br />\n由分手到依加，我間房都仲擺滿咗同佢嘅合照<br />\n仍然戴住屬於我同佢嘅情侶戒指<br />\n仍然好天真妄想有一日，會同佢復合<br />\n一等，就等咗八年。。。<br />\n<br />\n直到最近，我知道佢就嚟結婚。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢排成日夢遊<br />\n又去返好多以前同佢一齊去過嘅地方<br />\n每次都會不自覺咁諗返起同佢一齊果時嘅經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到底我應該點處理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4a497305aecc2d5990a68ccee07034252b94cc","tid":1481537,"uid":43381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:59:05.000Z","msg":"睇到有啲心痛<br />\n點解八年都唔能夠釋懷<br />\n你地曾經發生過咩經歷？"},{"pid":"0f5ef51cc648725cfb419c272b7f8d98b592dc5d","tid":1481537,"uid":299371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:01:18.000Z","msg":"放過自己呢"},{"pid":"640b209961ef7770060905a44552cd27ea36df9e","tid":1481537,"uid":299371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f5ef51cc648725cfb419c272b7f8d98b592dc5d","tid":1481537,"uid":299371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:01:18.000